{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Celestial Trails</strong> is a cozy life-sim adventure game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You arrive on a barren island in search of a fresh start. Gather resources, build your town, and unlock advanced technologies. Can you guide your society from the humble beginnings of stone and fire to the wonders of stars and galaxies?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Establish your settlement!</strong> Gather resources, farm, fish, craft tools, and build homes and workshops to grow your community.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unlock new technologies!</strong> Research advancements in resource management, water, electricity, and space travel to evolve your society.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Customize your world!</strong> Personalize your character, decorate buildings, and shape the island to reflect your vision.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Embark on an interstellar journey!</strong> Build a rocket to explore the stars.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Engage in mini-games!</strong> Participate in fun activities to earn rewards and new items.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3360130?t=1732511393","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3360130/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1732511393","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3360130/8805e26df73175df3a8abb208a988300fac2a20e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732511393","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3360130/8805e26df73175df3a8abb208a988300fac2a20e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1732511393","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"